<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink371">
<l>maḷḷar koṭṭiṉ maññai yālu</l>
<l>muyarneṭuṅ kuṉṟam paṭumaḻai talaiic</l>
<l>curanaṉi yiṉiya vākuka tilla</l>
<l>vaṟaneṟi yituveṉat teḷintaveṉ</l>
<l>piṟainutaṟ kuṟumakaḷ pōkiya kāṉē</l>
      </lg>
     <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>May the desert become indeed very pleasant, </l>
<l>[and] the heavy rain pour [like] in the high and long mountains, </l>
<l>where peacocks dance to the [drum]  beats of warriors –  </l>
<l>the desert where my small girl with crescent forehead went, </l>
<l>realising that it is the path of virtue. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
